3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with unsupervised video representation learning, which is a subfield of AI.
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with video prediction and generation, which are core topics in multimedia research.
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with motion dynamics and uncertainty, which are relevant to robotics research.
